race.description: Tabtouch Road To The Cup Handicap (Bm70+)
race.comment: TRUE CHANCE (5) has a strong fitness base now and looks ready to step out to the 1990m journey today. He's been closing strongly over the mile in his past couple and the inside draw today can see him sit a little closer. Rates highly off his form this campaign and can raise the bar again here. THE JESTER'S SON (4) comes here third-up and ready to strike as h steps out to this trip for the first time. His form at the end of last campaign in Kalgoorlie looks very strong for a race like this and he's building towards that this time in. Watch for him late in the race. MR TALENTINO (6) flew home to score over the mile here last start and is now third-up and out to a more suitable trip. He's outperformed his market expectation so far this campaign and that sets him up nicely for this. Maps well and can repeat the dose. WILD IMAGINATION (1) carries the top weight but is a classy customer and can't be discounted. UNCOMPROMISED (2) can feature third-up.
